Insider Activity


Individual




Mark van Mourick



Mr. Mark van Mourick is Chairman at Optivest Properties, LLC, Chief Executive Officer at Optivest, Inc., and Chairman at Optivest Foundation. He is on the Board of Directors at National Storage Affiliates Trust, Simple Signal, Inc., Northrise University Initiative, and Forest Home.
Mr. van Mourick was previously employed as Senior Vice President & Principal by Smith Barney Harris Upham & Co., Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Southern California.



