 Educational Background



Bachelor of Arts Degree in Business Management 


University of Southern California

                  University of Southern California is a private research university that mainly offers undergraduate, graduate & other higher education. The university was founded in 1880 and is headquartered in Los Angeles, CA.                





 Career History



Founder

                                    1993 - Current                


Optivest, Inc.


                  Optivest, Inc. is a private company headquartered in Dana Point, CA. The firm provides investment advice. It was founded by Mark van Mourick, he is the current CEO, occupying that position since 1987.                




