 Boards & Committees



Corporate Boards ▾




Trustee

                    2015 - Current                  


National Storage Affiliates Trust

                    National Storage Affiliates Trust operates as a real estate investment trust. It focuses on the ownership, operation, and acquisition of self-storage properties located within the top 100 metropolitan statistical areas throughout the United States. The company was founded by Arlen D. Nordhagen in April 2013 and is headquartered in Greenwood Village, CO.                  




Chairman

                    2007 - Current                  


Optivest Properties LLC






Director

                    Current                  


Simple Signal, Inc.

                    Simple Signal, Inc. provides cloud-based hosted unified communications and collaboration services to deliver voice, video, and mobile communications for businesses in the United States and Canada. It offers hosted PBX, enterprise unified communication, mobility, virtual call center, video and audio conferencing, integration, disaster recovery, analytics, video, virtual call center, backup and storage, fax to email, network services, SIP trunking, desktop, collaboration, and integration solutions; video PBX telephony over iPads, iPhones, and Android mobile devices that can connect with various brands of video conferencing equipment; and video conferencing products in an outsourced Video-as-a-Service solution without on-premise video infrastructure. The company was founded by Dave Gilbert in 2004 and is headquartered in Dana Point, CA.                  




